## Important folders

> Update this list as the project gains real folders. The defaults below come from the `{{preset_id}}` preset.

- `src/app` — app shell, routing, top-level orchestration.
- `src/features` — feature-specific UI and orchestration.
- `src/components/ui` — shadcn-style reusable visual primitives.
- `src/domain` — framework-independent business rules.
- `src/services` — IO wrappers (storage, HTTP, filesystem).
- `src/data` — local static data, JSON, fixtures.
- `src/config` — typed config and environment parsing.
- `src/lib` — small generic helpers.
- `src/tests` — shared test setup and integration tests.
- `docs` — durable project documentation.
- `scripts` — deterministic project utility scripts.

## Commands

| Command                 | Purpose                                                  |
| ----------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------- |
| `pnpm run dev`          | Start the development server.                            |
| `pnpm run typecheck`    | TypeScript checking.                                     |
| `pnpm run lint`         | ESLint.                                                  |
| `pnpm test`             | Vitest once.                                             |
| `pnpm run test:watch`   | Vitest in watch mode.                                    |
| `pnpm run build`        | Production build.                                        |
| `pnpm run verify`       | Typecheck + lint + test + build (commit gate).           |
| `pnpm dlx fallow ...`   | Deterministic dead-code / complexity / duplication scan. |

